/-! ## Uniqueness theorem -/


/-- **Uniqueness theorem.** Any level-1 weight-144 modular form `f` whose first 13
q-coefficients match the LMFDB-published values for `1.144.a.{a..}` is equal to our
explicit construction `lmfdb_1_144_a_orbit`. Proven via `ModularForm.eq_of_sturm_bound`. -/
